        <abstract> 
<p>Suggests WTT-D read account of <hi rend="italic">Bignonia capreolata</hi> in forthcoming <hi rend="italic">Climbing plants</hi>.</p>  
<p>Plans experiments [on Melastomataceae]. Describes similar experiment performed on <hi rend="italic">Monochaetum</hi>. Interested in meaning of differently coloured stamens.</p> 
        </abstract>
